'''天主教希維德尼察教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Suidniciensis}}；{{lang-pl|Diecezja świdnicka}}）是[[波蘭|波蘭]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教弗羅茨瓦夫總教區|弗羅茨瓦夫總教區]]。教座位於[[希維德尼察|希維德尼察]]。

教區於2004年2月24日成立<ref>{{cite web |title=SUIDNICIENSIS |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_20040224_multos-fructus.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2020-03-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200331142454/https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_20040224_multos-fructus.html |archivedate=2020-03-31 |language=la |date=2004-02-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2011年時有668,900名教友（佔轄區678,900人口中98.5%）、186個堂區、393名司鐸、109名修士和440名修女。現任教區主教為{{link-pl|瑪爾谷·門德克|Marek Mendyk}}<ref name="Vatican20200331">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 31.03.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/03/31/200331b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-03-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200331123711/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/03/31/200331b.html |archivedate=2020-03-31 |language=en |date=2020-03-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-pl|亞當·巴瓦布赫|Adam Bałabuch}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE (CONTINUAZIONE), 19.03.2008 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2008/03/19/0197/00456.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-03-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200331142117/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2008/03/19/0197/00456.html |archivedate=2020-03-31 |language=it |date=2008-03-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-pl|依納爵·德茨|Ignacy Dec}}<ref name="Vatican20200331" />。

